{"id":850,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":850,"title":"Ezekiel 22","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 22"],[".studySummary",["i","Ezekiel catalogs the sins of the people of Judah in Jerusalem—They will be scattered and destroyed for their iniquities."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.1","order":"02.27.022.56571"},["b","1"],"Moreover the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.2","order":"02.27.022.56572"},["b","2"],"Now, thou son of man, wilt thou judge, wilt thou judge the bloody city? yea, thou shalt shew her all her abominations."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.3","order":"02.27.022.56573"},["b","3"],"Then say thou, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", The city",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sheddeth"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"blood"],"in the midst of it, that her",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"time"],"may come, and maketh idols against herself to defile herself."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.4","order":"02.27.022.56574"},["b","4"],"Thou art become guilty in thy blood that thou hast shed; and hast defiled thyself in thine idols which thou hast made; and thou hast caused thy days to draw near, and art come",["i","even"],"unto thy years: therefore have I made thee a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"reproach"],"unto the heathen, and a mocking to all countries."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.5","order":"02.27.022.56575"},["b","5"],["i","Those that be"],"near, and",["i","those that be"],"far from thee, shall mock thee,",["i","which art"],"infamous",["i","and"],"much vexed."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.6","order":"02.27.022.56576"},["b","6"],"Behold, the princes of Israel, every one were in thee to their power to shed blood."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.7","order":"02.27.022.56577"},["b","7"],"In thee have they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"set light by"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"father"],"and mother: in the midst of thee have they dealt by",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"oppression"],"with the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"stranger"],": in thee have they vexed the fatherless and the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_7e"},"widow"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.8","order":"02.27.022.56578"},["b","8"],"Thou hast despised mine holy things, and hast profaned my sabbaths."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.9","order":"02.27.022.56579"},["b","9"],"In thee are men that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"carry tales to"],"shed blood: and in thee they eat upon the mountains: in the midst of thee they commit",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"lewdness"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.10","order":"02.27.022.56580"},["b","10"],"In thee have they discovered their fathers’",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"nakedness"],": in thee have they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"humbled"],"her that was set",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"apart"],"for",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"pollution"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.11","order":"02.27.022.56581"},["b","11"],"And one hath committed abomination with his neighbour’s wife; and another hath lewdly defiled his daughter in law; and another in thee hath humbled his sister, his father’s daughter."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.12","order":"02.27.022.56582"},["b","12"],"In thee have they taken",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"gifts"],"to shed blood; thou hast taken",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"usury"],"and increase, and thou hast greedily gained of thy neighbours by extortion, and hast forgotten me, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.13","order":"02.27.022.56583"},["b","13"],"¶Behold, therefore I have smitten mine hand at thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"dishonest"],"gain which thou hast made, and at thy blood which hath been in the midst of thee."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.14","order":"02.27.022.56584"},["b","14"],"Can thine heart endure, or can thine hands be strong, in the days that I shall deal with thee? I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have spoken",["i","it,"],"and will do",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.15","order":"02.27.022.56585"},["b","15"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"scatter"],"thee among the heathen, and disperse thee in the countries, and will consume thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"filthiness"],"out of thee."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.16","order":"02.27.022.56586"},["b","16"],"And thou shalt take thine inheritance in thyself in the sight of the heathen, and thou shalt know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.17","order":"02.27.022.56587"},["b","17"],"And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.18","order":"02.27.022.56588"},["b","18"],"Son of man, the house of Israel is to me become",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"dross"],": all they",["i","are"],"brass, and tin, and iron, and lead, in the midst of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"furnace"],"; they are",["i","even"],"the dross of silver."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.19","order":"02.27.022.56589"},["b","19"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Because ye are all become dross, behold, therefore I will gather you into the midst of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.20","order":"02.27.022.56590"},["b","20"],["i","As"],"they gather silver, and brass, and iron, and lead, and tin, into the midst of the furnace, to blow the fire upon it, to melt",["i","it;"],"so will I gather",["i","you"],"in mine anger and in my fury, and I will leave",["i","you there,"],"and melt you."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.21","order":"02.27.022.56591"},["b","21"],"Yea, I will gather you, and blow upon you in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"fire"],"of my wrath, and ye shall be melted in the midst thereof."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.22","order":"02.27.022.56592"},["b","22"],"As silver is melted in the midst of the furnace, so shall ye be melted in the midst thereof; and ye shall know that I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have poured out my fury upon you."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.23","order":"02.27.022.56593"},["b","23"],"¶And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.24","order":"02.27.022.56594"},["b","24"],"Son of man, say unto her, Thou",["i","art"],"the land that is not cleansed, nor",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"rained"],"upon in the day of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"indignation"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.25","order":"02.27.022.56595"},["b","25"],["i","There is"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"conspiracy"],"of her",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"prophets"],"in the midst thereof, like a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"roaring lion"],"ravening the prey; they have devoured souls; they have taken the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_25d"},"treasure"],"and",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_25e"},"precious"],"things; they have made her many widows in the midst thereof."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.26","order":"02.27.022.56596"},["b","26"],"Her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"priests"],"have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"violated"],"my law, and have profaned mine holy things: they have put no",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"difference"],"between the holy and profane, neither have they shewed",["i","difference"],"between the unclean and the clean, and have hid their eyes from my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_26d"},"sabbaths"],", and I am",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_26e"},"profaned"],"among them."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.27","order":"02.27.022.56597"},["b","27"],"Her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"princes"],"in the midst thereof",["i","are"],"like wolves ravening the prey, to shed blood,",["i","and"],"to destroy souls, to get dishonest",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"gain"],"."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.28","order":"02.27.022.56598"},["b","28"],"And her prophets have daubed them with untempered",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"mortar"],","],"seeing vanity, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"divining"],"lies unto them, saying, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", when the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath not spoken."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.29","order":"02.27.022.56599"},["b","29"],"The people of the land have used oppression, and exercised robbery, and have vexed the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"poor"],"and needy: yea, they have oppressed the stranger wrongfully."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.30","order":"02.27.022.56600"},["b","30"],"And I sought for a man among them, that should make up the hedge, and stand in the gap before me for the land, that I should not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"destroy"],"it: but I found none."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.31","order":"02.27.022.56601"},["b","31"],"Therefore have I poured out mine indignation upon them; I have consumed them with the fire of my wrath: their own way have I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"recompensed"],"upon their heads, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.3a","order":"02.27.022.56602"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.18.16-20"},"Ezek. 36:18 (16–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.3b","order":"02.27.022.56604"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-shedding-of"},"TG Blood, Shedding of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.3c","order":"02.27.022.56606"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.25"},"Ezek. 21:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.4a","order":"02.27.022.56608"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.14"},"Ezek. 5:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.7a","order":"02.27.022.56610"},["b","7a"],["span.small","HEB"],"treated lightly or dishonored."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.7b","order":"02.27.022.56612"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honoring-father-and-mother"},"TG Honoring Father and Mother"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.7c","order":"02.27.022.56614"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.10.9-11"},"Zech. 7:10 (9–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.7d","order":"02.27.022.56616"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"TG Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"7e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.7e","order":"02.27.022.56618"},["b","7e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.12"},"Amos 5:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/6.39.37-40"},"Hel. 6:39 (37–40)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.9a","order":"02.27.022.56620"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"slander in order to."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.9b","order":"02.27.022.56622"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sensuality"},"TG Sensuality"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.10a","order":"02.27.022.56624"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/18.7.7-8"},"Lev. 18:7 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.10b","order":"02.27.022.56626"},["b","10b"],["span.small","HEB"],"abused her who is unclean in her time of menstruation."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.10c","order":"02.27.022.56628"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/18.19"},"Lev. 18:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.10d","order":"02.27.022.56630"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.17.16-20"},"Ezek. 36:17 (16–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.12a","order":"02.27.022.56632"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.25"},"Deut. 27:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.23"},"Isa. 1:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.12b","order":"02.27.022.56634"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.14"},"Isa. 3:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/3.10"},"Amos 3:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/4.12.12-13"},"Alma 4:12 (12–13)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/usury"},"TG Usury"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.13a","order":"02.27.022.56636"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.15a","order":"02.27.022.56638"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-ten-lost-tribes-of"},"Israel, Ten Lost Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.15b","order":"02.27.022.56640"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/filthiness"},"TG Filthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.18a","order":"02.27.022.56642"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.119"},"Ps. 119:119"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.18b","order":"02.27.022.56644"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/48.10"},"Isa. 48:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.21a","order":"02.27.022.56646"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.31"},"Ezek. 21:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.24a","order":"02.27.022.56648"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/68.9"},"Ps. 68:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.26"},"Ezek. 34:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.24b","order":"02.27.022.56650"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-indignation-of"},"TG God, Indignation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.25a","order":"02.27.022.56652"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conspiracy"},"TG Conspiracy"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.25b","order":"02.27.022.56654"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"TG False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"25c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.25c","order":"02.27.022.56656"},["b","25c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/28.15"},"Prov. 28:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"25d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.25d","order":"02.27.022.56658"},["b","25d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"25e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.25e","order":"02.27.022.56660"},["b","25e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.5"},"Jer. 20:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.26a","order":"02.27.022.56662"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.26b","order":"02.27.022.56664"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/2.8"},"Mal. 2:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"26c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.26c","order":"02.27.022.56666"},["b","26c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/10.10"},"Lev. 10:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.23"},"Ezek. 44:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"26d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.26d","order":"02.27.022.56668"},["b","26d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/17.27.22,24,27"},"Jer. 17:27 (22, 24, 27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.24"},"Ezek. 44:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"26e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.26e","order":"02.27.022.56670"},["b","26e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/profanity"},"TG Profanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.27a","order":"02.27.022.56672"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kings-earthly"},"TG Kings, Earthly"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.27b","order":"02.27.022.56674"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.29"},"2 Ne. 26:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/4-ne/1.26"},"4 Ne. 1:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.28a","order":"02.27.022.56676"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.10"},"Ezek. 13:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.28b","order":"02.27.022.56678"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/superstitions"},"TG Superstitions"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.29a","order":"02.27.022.56680"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor"},"TG Poor"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.30a","order":"02.27.022.56682"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.26"},"Gen. 18:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.1"},"Jer. 5:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.31a","order":"02.27.022.56684"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.4"},"Ezek. 7:4"],"."]]}
